OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Ffine and dry this evening with plenty
OL,7,Fof late sunshine. Little change
OL,8,Fovernight with largely clear skies,
OL,9,Fbut still a notable easterly breeze
OL,10,Ftowards the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother largely dry and
OL,13,Fsunny day across the region. A very
OL,14,Fsmall chance of the odd thunderstorm
OL,15,Fdeveloping later, mainly towards
OL,16,FCornwall. Feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
