OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining largely dry and settled
OL,7,Fthroughout. A small chance of the odd
OL,8,Fthundery shower Thursday, but most
OL,9,Fwill avoid them. Very warm initially
OL,10,Fbut turning less warm by Saturday.
